high_descs: Step forward and turn left to face the center table.
Pick up the knife on the center table.
Take a step to the right to face the bread on the counter.
Cut the bread on the counter into slices.
Turn left and walk forward to face the trash can on the left.
Place the knife in the trash can.
Turn around to face the bread on the center table.
Pick up a slice of bread on the counter.
Turn right and walk forward to face the microwave.
Heat the bread slice in the microwave and remove  it.
Turn around and walk around to face the trash can in the corner of the room.
Place the bread slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: To heat a slice of bread and place it in the trash can.

high_descs: Go to the kitchen island ahead and to your left.
Pick up the knife between the loaf of bread and the knife, on the island.
Move over to the loaf of bread, on the island, to your right.
Cut the loaf of bread, on the island, into slices.
Turn to your left and go to the garbage bin, on your left, past the refrigerator, and on the floor.
Put the knife in the garbage bin, on the floor.
Turn to your left and go back to the loaf of bread on the island, to your left.
Pick up one of the slices of bread from the island.
Turn to your right and go to the microwave, above the stove, across from you.
Place the slice of bread in the microwave, heat it up, then remove the slice of bread from the microwave.
Turn to your right and go to the corner, then turn to your right again and go past the refrigerator, to the garbage bin past the refrigerator, to your right.
Place the slice of bread in the garbage bin on the floor.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife and a warm slice of bread in the garbage bin.

high_descs: Turn left to to go the island on the left.
Pick up the yellow knife on the right of the hand sculpture.
Move over right to the bread.
Slice a half of the bread on the counter.
Turn left and go to the black trash can on the floor in the left corner.
Place the knife in the trash can.
Turn left and go back the to island with the sliced bread.
Pick up one slice of the bread from the counter.
Turn right and go to he microwave above the stove.
Remove the bread after heating it in the microwave.
Turn right and go back to the black trash can in the corner.
Place the bread in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Throw out a heated slice of bread.
